*mailwrapper-0.2.1 (15 Dec 2004)

  15 Dec 2004; Grant Goodyear <g2boojum@gentoo.org>
  +mailwrapper-0.2.1.ebuild:
  New version fixes up man pages to point to /etc/mail/mailer.conf instead
  of /etc/mailer.conf.  Leaving all keywords the same since the changes
  were only to the man pages.  Closes bug 53234.  Thanks to Nick Fisher
  and Luke Macken.

  28 Sep 2004; Andrej Kacian <ticho@gentoo.org> metadata.xml:
  Fixed herd name in metadata.xml.

*mailwrapper-0.2 (30 May 2004)

